      • execute

        CompletableFuture<Result<O>> execute(ServiceContext<I> serviceContext)
        Execute associated action using the input.
        Parameters:
        serviceContext - Request context (Request ID, Bank ID, password, redirect URLs, etc.) and associated services (Encryption, Consent access, etc.)
        Returns:
        The outcome of the executed action that will be parsed by Facade.
